    <div class="container">
      <div class="poster card">
        <img src="/images/sample.png" alt="Event Poster" class="poster-img"/>
      </div>
      
      <div class="description">
        <h2 class="text-2xl  font-dirtyline">face painting</h2>
        <p style="text-align: left;">Description:</p>
        <p>ahjskhjsdhljdckdjks ahnjsgjdkahjdka Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Cum id voluptates nostrum veritatis at, accusantium natus incidunt recusandae voluptatum. Porro accusantium pariatur dignissimos iste eveniet odit unde optio laborum vero.</p>
